app.long_description:
Commiters: GerbilSoft, JoostinOnline, GreyRogue, Howard, Cyan, nastys
Project website: https://github.com/brunochanrio/Nintendont-MametchiKitty
Nintendont-MametchiKitty allows you to run GameCube games on a Wii or Wii U from an SD or HDD device.
